{"id": "1368799582624157908", "channel_id": "1368526930017783850", "type": 0, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "打擊、防禦的數值錯誤，打擊是20%攻擊、防禦是20%防禦並且獲得的狂氣都是10點，指令卡一的效果不太合理，你給敵人上20層毒自己也要吃20層毒？數值太低負面效果太高，改為每有一名上40層毒，自身收到20%層數的毒", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T04:00:51.564000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368526930017783850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉唤醒体DIY", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1366599688257802311"]}
{"id": "1368898760737816607", "channel_id": "1368526930017783850", "type": 0, "author_id": "845605732702748684", "author_name": "y_win7", "author_bot": false, "content": "谢谢大佬指正，私密马赛，小登还没研究清楚数值所以乱填了，才知道打击和防御的数值如何计算得出，长知识了🥹 \n指令卡一效果是考虑到如果战斗里敌方没有给自身上毒则启灵三其实就无作用了，想着启灵三可以增加以自身作为毒引爆器的机制，多一种玩法\n当然如果没有抽到三启就拿去换50黑印吧（？🥴 \n不过大佬的提议改法也有趣，只是担心这样一来容易把自己毒死，考虑到伤转毒，毒有可能会比血量高🤔", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T10:34:57.469000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T10:35:26.493000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368526930017783850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉唤醒体DIY", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1366599688257802311"]}
{"id": "1368922365735604284", "channel_id": "1368922365735604284", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "# Why not stack strength and tentacle damage via full aqua team?\nI find tentacle damage + tentacle amount + tentacle assembly stacking to be underwhelming when faced with end game bosses will millions of HP so I want to stack team crit instead and hope it deals at least 2m damage.\n\n# Team crit buff list:\nTulu: exalt 25% temporary crit rate, 3 cost 15% temporary crit rate \nCorpo: exalt 20% crit damage + 10% per death res trigger \nCorpo wheel: 20% temporary crit damage + 1 per tentacle \nHorla: exalt 28% temporary crit rate and damage, overexalt 58% instead. \nMiryam wheel: 15% temporary crit damage \nTo my dearest friend wheel: 25% temporary crit rate \nMurphy event wheel: 10% temporary crit rate and damage per posse\nRat: exalt 70% temporary crit damage\nGoliath posse: 15% crit rate and damage \n\n# Putting the numbers together:\nAssume exalt all, posse x2  [if cat notes is true we can do that], 10 tentacles, 1 death res trigger:\nI'll ignore Crit rate math as it is far over 100%.\n**Crit Damage:**\n70x2 [rat exalt] +\n20+number of tentacles x2 [corpo wheel] +\n10x2 [Murphy event wheel] + \n15 [Miryam wheel] +\n15 [Goliath posse] +\n20+10xdeath res triggers [corpo exalt] + \n58 [horla overexalt]\n= 343% crit damage", "timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:08:45.339000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-05T12:10:23.768000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1368922366280994816", "filename": "Screenshot_20250505_192759_Morimens.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1245396, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368922365735604284/1368922366280994816/Screenshot_20250505_192759_Morimens.png?ex=69cbb94d&is=69ca67cd&hm=7fa04c9d454443dc2bc8302c683e06c8cf400ea1097ba4eb1c2bf95e12b59888&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368922365735604284", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Crit Build Theory Crafting", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
